{"type": "assistant", "message": {"id": "msg_1784876398071", "type": "message", "role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "太好了！这非常有价值。通过 free-search 找到的关键先验工作如下：\n\n1. **\"When Humans Growl and Birds Speak\"** (arXiv:2505.24336, Interspeech 2025) — 作者包括 Minsu Kang, Seolhee Lee, Choonghyeon Lee, Namhyun Cho — **与当前论文的作者相同**。这篇论文很可能就是 \"humansgrowl\" 引用的 H2NH-VC 基线模型。\n2. **\"Unleash Your Inner Monster\"** (Interspeech 2025) — 另一篇来自同一团队的 H2NH-VC 演示论文。\n3. **\"Speak Like a Dog\"** (arXiv:2206.04780, 2022) — 早期的 H2NH-VC 工作，提出了这项任务。\n4. **laion/character-voices** — 包含 14 种角色原型的现有角色语音数据集。\n\n让我来获取更多关于这些关键先验工作的详细信息。"}], "model": "GLM-5.2-w4a8", "stop_reason": null, "stop_sequence": null, "usage": {"input_tokens": 0, "output_tokens": 0, "cache_creation_input_tokens": 0, "cache_read_input_tokens": 0}, "context_management": null}, "parent_tool_use_id": null, "session_id": "e45974bb-b816-4fcf-a9b3-335d4c1c9cf1", "uuid": "efe48dc6-4ce8-45c6-83cc-ac2636071971"}
